OL,3,CResidents say General Election should
OL,4,Cfocus on the economy and climate change
OL,6,FResidents in the Scottish Borders have
OL,7,Fbeen sharing what key priorities
OL,8,Fpolitical parties should be
OL,9,Fconsidering ahead of the next General
OL,10,FElection - including a focus on the
OL,11,Feconomy, and on climate change.
OL,13,FSue Briggs, of The General Store,
OL,14,Fwants to see more focus on the link
OL,15,Fbetween large companies, the climate
OL,16,Fcrisis and reducing waste.
