OL,3,CResidents say General Election should
OL,4,Cfocus on the economy and climate change
OL,6,F"I'd actually like to see a policy
OL,7,Flevel, the government thinking about
OL,8,Fhow to make the link between things
OL,9,Flike repairing stuff and climate
OL,10,Fchange.
OL,12,F"We know that landfill contributes to
OL,13,Fclimate change, but maybe people don't
OL,14,Fmake the link between being able to
OL,15,Fget their possessions repaired and
OL,16,Fpersonally doing something about the
OL,17,Fclimate problem," she said.
