OL,6,FMs Briggs said: "I'd like them to work
OL,7,Fon making that link clearer for
OL,8,Fpeople. I would like the next UK
OL,9,Fgovernment to take seriously this idea
OL,10,Fof your right to repair.
OL,12,F"So what I mean by that is I would
OL,13,Flike them to put pressure on big
OL,14,Fmanufacturers in particular to provide
OL,15,Fspare parts to make it possible to get
OL,16,Finto things and fix them, to give
OL,17,Finstructions on how to do because at
OL,18,Fthe moment there's not enough of that
OL,19,Fgoing on and too much landfill."
