OL,3,CResidents say General Election should
OL,4,Cfocus on the economy and climate change
OL,6,FPrime Minister Rishi Sunak made the
OL,7,Fannouncement of a general election on
OL,8,FWednesday 22 May - meaning MPs have
OL,9,Fonly six weeks on the campaign trail.
OL,11,FThe seat for Berwickshire, Roxburgh
OL,12,Fand Selkirk has been held by John
OL,13,FLamont, a Conservative MP since June
OL,14,F2017.
OL,16,FSophie Hill, a voter in Selkirk, told
OL,17,FITV Border: "I think climate change
OL,18,Fand action and proper policies on
OL,19,Fclimate change will be highly
OL,20,Fimportant this election and especially
OL,21,Ffor the younger people.
