OL,3,CResidents say General Election should
OL,4,Cfocus on the economy and climate change
OL,6,F"I think the younger people now
OL,7,Funderstand that climate change is
OL,8,Freally going to affect their future
OL,9,Fand their children's future in a way
OL,10,Fthat hasn't really been engaged with
OL,11,Fbefore."
OL,13,FThe last general election took place
OL,14,Fon 12 December 2019, where seven
OL,15,FConservative MPs and one Liberal
OL,16,FDemocrat MP were elected across the
OL,17,FITV Border region.
